Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,A
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.32,0:00:07.99,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,We made it to Venice! {Line 2 and 3 are the same as Episode 18 -Gyro}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.57,0:00:09.53,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I'm diving into the canal!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.84,0:00:26.26,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Mista! \NGet out of the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.56,0:00:37.89,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,G-Giorno! \NY-You're... already starting to...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.23,0:00:44.15,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,As I'm sure you're aware, Mista,\Nour top priority is to retrieve the object.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:47.03,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Our success lies in its retrieval!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:53.66,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,The disc is right inside it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.08,0:00:57.62,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Since we're surrounded by such a large body of water, \Nit will take longer for him to freeze the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:00:58.75,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,That's why I did this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.75,0:01:00.83,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me! \NHurry and get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:04.71,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,I hear you, Giorno!\NBut your idea of success doesn't do it for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:08.97,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Killing him, then the two of us\Ngetting what we came here for... {Totally fine if you want to revert, I just hate "the object" -G}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.97,0:01:10.17,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Now {\i1}that's{\i0} a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.64,0:01:16.22,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Like fucking hell you'll get off that easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:24.65,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Go right ahead and jump in, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.65,0:01:30.74,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I'll take my chances on whether or not\Nyou can outswim my ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:35.78,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,N-No! \NDriving into the canal was a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:40.00,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,The way he uses ice... is unbeatable!
Comment: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:40.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Opening
