Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:16.84,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,{\an8}Turn the car into a plant, Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:20.14,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,The hood hasn't completely frozen up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:23.89,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,So hurry up and grow some plants \Nwhile you can still create life!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:31.07,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Trying to grow vines to use as ropes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:33.74,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Fuck that shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:38.28,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I-It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:42.95,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,As I thought, in order to make a vine that will grow fast enough to reach the bank, I need heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:48.00,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,At this temperature, only short grass \Nlike you'd find in a tundra can sustain life!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:51.13,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Who said anything about using them\Nto reach the bank, Giorno?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:53.38,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,This'll do just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.38,0:03:55.05,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Short grass is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:03:58.38,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,But I need more! More! A lot more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:00.93,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Keep making more if you wanna live!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.93,0:04:04.35,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,We're gonna die if you don't hurry up, Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:10.40,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Gotcha! \NSucks that it didn't grow to the bank of the canal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:13.69,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,You did it, Giorno!\N It froze over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:16.03,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Now you're saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:25.20,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Th-That fucker! \NHe made me freeze the grass and turn it into a sled?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:28.04,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,N-No... A snowboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:29.37,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Fucking dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:32.50,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,He's not gonna let me off that easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:33.21,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Of course not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:37.76,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,White Album! \NTemporarily unfreeze the ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:41.55,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Th-The ice...{lol CR actually had "Th ice". -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:42.76,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,...melted!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:45.52,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:53.40,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,This is the static world of sub zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:56.28,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Nothing can move at temperatures this low!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:57.94,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,It fucks everything up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:05:02.74,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,That's why my White Album is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:07.45,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I could stop the whole fucking ocean if I wanted to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:10.96,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Hurry and reach the bank, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:16.25,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:18.21,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Gather up the grass floating in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.84,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,The grass you were using as a snowboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:21.80,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Do it while you can still fire with your right hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.47,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Just give up, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:29.23,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Don't you get that attacking me is fucking pointless?!{Oh my god, I know I said Ghiacchio is Dio now last week, but I didn't expect him to commit to that so quickly. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:40.61,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Gathering up grass... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:46.62,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Giorno, if you release your ability, \Nthe short grass will turn back into car parts...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.83,0:05:51.37,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,...which makes them perfect for attacking him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:52.62,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:02.34,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,D-Did that finish him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:04.01,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,No, too shallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:06.05,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,We only have a temporary reprieve from the danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:08.72,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,But Mista, you've bought us precious time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:12.52,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Let's quickly grab the object, then get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:15.94,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,We won't be able to employ the same strategy\Nif he catches us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:19.11,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Please go, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:22.65,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,The disc should show up somewhere\Nif I destroy the lion statue...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:25.20,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,I'll snatch it and hide in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:26.95,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,If I have a few dozen seconds, I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:30.66,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,But will hiding be enough to lose him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:34.75,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,I think it will work, but I could be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:38.04,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Either way, this guy is seriously bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:42.80,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,If he runs into Buccellati and the others... That would be the worst case scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:45.38,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,We need to finish this here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:47.60,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,It's our only chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:50.22,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Wha...?! \NMista! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:53.68,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Your ability is perfect? Yeah right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:58.90,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,If you're totally encased in ice,\Nthen just how are you breathing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:04.74,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,That's it. I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:06.45,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Air's leaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:10.08,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,He's breathing from a hole at the back of his neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:12.50,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Get into position, Sex Pistols!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:16.17,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Number One and Number Two, \Ngo around and flank him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:20.38,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,He's lookin' right at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:23.09,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,He's gonna use another ice attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:26.76,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,No, he's gonna go up for air first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:30.14,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Once he reaches the surface,\NI'm gonna fire right into his breathing hole!{Oops. A CR mistranslation that I missed the first time around. He says he'll "shove bullets into the hole", not "shoot a hole in his head". -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:31.72,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,He's trying to surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.31,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Here we go, Pistols!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:35.94,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,We have to time this for\N the instant he takes a breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.94,0:07:37.06,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:40.90,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Number One and Two say they can't see the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:45.74,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,It's how he's swimming! \NHe's looking up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:47.36,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,It's hiding the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:50.45,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,O-Oh no! Let's scram!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:51.78,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,That's enough, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:55.66,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Hold your position, \NNumber One and Number Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:58.92,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Did you seriously hit my fucking forehead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:07:59.96,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:07.01,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,The fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:09.30,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,You shot at the fish swimming around me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:11.97,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,What the fuck are you trying to pull?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:13.89,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,He looked down! We can see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:15.47,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,It's the hole! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:17.44,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:19.23,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,We got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:26.78,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Hooray! Bullseye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:35.79,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Th-That noise...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:38.50,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,That noise... It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:43.29,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,So you found my breathing hole\Nand decided to target it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:45.09,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:47.88,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Too bad temperatures this low stop everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:52.55,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Gases turn to liquids, and liquids turn to solids!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.89,0:08:56.27,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Get a good look. \NSee how there's no airflow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:57.81,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,The bullet, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:09:01.85,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,That's the sound of a ricocheting bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:02.65,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:07.74,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,White Album: Gently Weeps! {https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bI8P6ZSHSvE}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:08.78,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:12.11,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I had already created a wall of frozen air!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:19.04,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,It uses up a good chunk of my Stand's power, \Nbut now you won't even be able to shoot a bolt into my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:21.54,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,It stops anything that comes near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:25.13,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,You're the one who made me learn my lesson, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.84,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Giorno was right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:31.59,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,This is all my fault... \NIt's my responsibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.43,0:09:35.64,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,I should have focused on getting the object...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:39.98,Thoughts,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,It's not under the trash can or bench...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.98,0:09:45.56,Thoughts,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Nothing that seems important,\Nand it's not like they'd hide it out in the open, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:51.78,Thoughts,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,But based on how Mista was running around,\Nit must be somewhere it can be found quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:55.74,Thoughts,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Where is it? \NThis photo should be a hint...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:59.08,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,This is bad. \NOur situation is dire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.08,0:10:01.46,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,Mista's beginning to act out of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:04.67,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,He's decided to take full responsibility for this, \Neven at the cost of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:13.34,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,But only those who possess true resolve\Ncan forge a path through the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:14.93,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,This is getting interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:18.76,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,Self sacrifice will be necessary at worst,\Nbut if Mista and I share the responsibility for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:21.56,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,...our combined resolve will forge a path!
Comment: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:24.06,Main,,0,0,0,,C
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:30.19,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,What the fuck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:32.24,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,It was in here the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:34.91,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Hiding inside the statue?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:36.45,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:42.00,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,If I get close enough, \NI should be able to shoot another bullet into his neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:44.83,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,I just need to be able to aim through his wall of air...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:47.54,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Mista's become reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:50.80,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,He's willing to take responsibility for this\Nat the cost of his own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:54.05,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,But what we need isn't bravery \Nborn from being backed into a corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:55.43,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,It's resolve!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.43,0:10:57.18,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,What we need right now is resolve!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.18,0:11:00.39,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Resolve doesn't mean sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.68,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,A computer disc!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:03.68,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:07.69,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,You were looking for something\Nto lead you to the boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:11.78,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I fucking did it!\NNow we can go expose the boss's true identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.78,0:11:15.24,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,All that's left now... is Trish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:17.45,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I'll take care of her after finishing you motherfuckers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:21.99,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Come on! \NFight until you lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:23.70,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I'll finish you assholes off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:25.58,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.63,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,What the fuck are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:42.81,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Resolve is the ability to forge a path\Nthrough the darkest night!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:50.31,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Guido Mista: Arrested at age seventeen for murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:52.78,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The result of the trial...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:59.11,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,His plea that he acted out of self-defense was rejected, and he was sentenced fifteen to thirty years in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.12,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,My happy-go-lucky youth...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:06.91,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,Is this really my fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:13.88,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Mista's outlook on life had always been optimistic, \Nbut at this moment, his head was buried in his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:20.22,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:23.39,Flashback,Guard,0,0,0,,Get up. You're being released.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:33.86,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,You're the one who bailed me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:38.74,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,Yes. I saw the incident on the news\Nand was convinced you acted out of self-defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:44.58,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,To keep it short, I see how passionate you are and know how skilled you are at gunslinging.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:49.50,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,But someone like you\Nwouldn't last two years in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:50.21,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,Which is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:53.29,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,You pulled some strings for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:55.17,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,Are you part of some organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:56.96,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:12:59.84,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,There's an excellent ristorante nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:15.23,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,You have quite the appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:18.11,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,The bruschetta here is great, too. \NDo you still have room for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:19.15,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:19.86,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:20.45,Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:23.91,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,Could you get him some... \NActually, for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:25.91,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,Could you get us four orders of bruschetta?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:30.75,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,Actually, make that five. \NI'll have some, too, while we're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:32.46,Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Right away, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:35.34,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,So, to pick up where we left off...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.34,0:13:36.42,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:39.01,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,I think the two of us will get along great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.01,0:13:40.92,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,So count me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:41.76,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,On one condition, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:46.18,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,Treat me to some dolce, too.{And his master?} \N Does this place have strawberry cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:49.43,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,You're a strange man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:57.48,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,I guess this is fate, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:14:01.15,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,Well, this isn't so bad, I guess. \NEverything worked out in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:06.37,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Mista learned that everyone's destiny is pre-determined.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:11.37,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Though people tend to stall \Nor take detours when they're young...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:16.17,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,...they ultimately end up traveling\N the path they were destined to take.{Just confirming what Gyro was asking, yes, the Japanese phrasing here and on the previous line is 1=1 with episode 8. -Starfish}{As of the TV version, these three are all copied from 8 -T}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:21.22,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,I see it! The path I need to take!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:24.09,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,This time I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:26.14,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,It's there, Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.14,0:14:29.60,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,I can see the path I gotta take through the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:36.15,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Yeehaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:48.28,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,You fuckheads just don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:52.79,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,The air is frozen because of how low the temperature is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:54.25,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:59.63,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,If I let air that's been frozen solid\Ninto my suit and let it melt...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.63,0:15:01.55,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,...it turns back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:03.55,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,If I take it in like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.22,0:15:06.84,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Just like a diver with an air tank strapped to their back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:09.68,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,...I don't need a breathing hole anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:11.06,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Th-The hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:13.06,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,He deflected the bullets!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:15.27,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,All six of 'em! O-Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:20.27,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,You better have the fucking resolve for this, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:27.20,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:30.87,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Yeah, my resolve is there, Giorno...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.87,0:15:35.04,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,If you hadn't given me your resolve, \NI wouldn't have seen this path....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.04,0:15:39.59,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,The resolve to take a path\Nwhere I'm willingly shot by my own bullets...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:45.13,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I-I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:47.18,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,The blood froze and hardened to my face...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:49.22,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,My path through the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.22,0:15:53.60,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,...wasn't the one where my bullets\Npenetrated your wall of ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:57.94,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,I-It was the one where\NI splattered your face with my blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:16:00.27,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Shit! I can't get it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:05.90,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Hey, the metal pole from earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.86,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Mista, your bullet shaped it into a{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:12.58,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Ow! That fucking hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:17.92,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Something... Something... Something... \NSomething warm is{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:21.75,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,You asked me if I had the resolve for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.09,0:16:24.80,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Well, I'm about to show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:27.55,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,But you'll have to show some resolve of your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:33.22,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,The resolve to be shot full of holes\Nand leave for the next world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:35.81,Thoughts,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Th-The fucker's still standing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:38.98,Thoughts,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,He's hell-bent on shoving me further back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:41.44,Thoughts,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Is he fucking nuts?!\NHe's gonna push my neck into the spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:44.15,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Shit! I need to get this out of my neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:51.66,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,You're crazy! \NThe bullet's gonna come flying back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:53.58,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,You're not gonna last!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:55.12,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,I have to make it through...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.12,0:16:57.29,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,This is my true resolve!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:16:59.87,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Pistols, steel yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:08.84,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,White Album: Gently Weeps!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.81,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Y-You can't take any more, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:22.19,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,You're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:23.94,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,And that'll mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:25.23,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,...we'll die, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:26.78,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,N-Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:30.82,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,I'm still conscious! \NI can still shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:36.91,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Y-You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:39.71,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,It went all the way in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.71,0:17:41.62,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,You're... wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:47.92,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,The one with stronger resolve... is me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:50.42,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Guido Mista...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.01,0:17:56.68,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I'll commend you for...\Ndriving me so far up against the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:18:01.39,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,But the one who took better advantage \Nof all the blood splatter... was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:06.02,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I froze the blood that spurted out of my neck\Nto keep me fixed in place!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:09.07,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Now my neck can't be\Npushed any farther into the spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:10.36,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I'm completely secured!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:13.24,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,The spike won't go any farther!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:15.95,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Also... Aren't you forgetting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:18.58,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,The last bullet you shot is still...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:21.96,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Right in the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:23.50,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:26.42,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,There's no wound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:31.63,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Wha{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.97,0:18:35.80,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Mista...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:44.44,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Your resolve is illuminating the path, \Nshining even brighter than the rising sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:47.61,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,And it's shining on the path...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:49.69,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,...that we're meant to take!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:53.07,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,What the fuck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.78,0:18:58.87,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Muda Muda Muda Muda!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:18.26,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Recently... I started noticing... that even though Giorno Giovanna... is so new at this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:24.56,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,...things always seem...\Nto play out exactly how he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.02,0:19:28.27,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,The resolve I showed just now \Nwas also partly Giorno's.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:32.61,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,It made its way into my heart\Nbefore I realized it had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:36.66,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,He almost feels more like my capo than Buccellati does.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:38.28,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,He drove me to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:41.03,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,What's the deal with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:43.16,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Well, I guess now's not the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:45.96,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,It's not my style to dwell on stuff like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:54.34,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Mista, we safely retrieved the disc thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:57.97,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Hurry up and heal me.\N I-I can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:20:02.76,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have found that resolve\Nif I didn't have faith in your ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:06.44,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Hurry up and heal me before I die...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:11.19,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Of course. \NBut I need to make something clear to you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:15.32,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Gold Experience's ability\Ndoesn't exactly have healing properties.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.32,0:20:17.32,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,It recreates parts of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:21.95,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,My plan is to imbue the bullets embedded in your body with life\Nand to plug up your arteries and other injured areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:23.91,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Just quit talking and do it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:27.79,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Since I'm not exactly healing you, \Nyour pain will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:29.88,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Please don't complain to me later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:32.21,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:37.88,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,O-Oww! Be more gentle! \NJesus, be more gentle Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:40.01,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I told you, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:42.64,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,You're a gangster for crying out loud, so quit fussing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.64,0:20:47.18,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,You have about eighteen more wounds, \Nso you'll need to remove your clothes for me to take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:54.11,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Buccellati! \NI'm picking up two signals...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:56.28,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Doesn't look like there's anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.28,0:20:57.74,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Proceed with caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:21:01.24,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I can only assume it's Mista and Giorno.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:04.95,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,They must be bored out of their minds waiting for us\Nif it went so smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:06.41,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Ah! Giorno!
